Note that the only purpose of $$k_1$$ is to define unambiguously $$u_{R0}$$. We can redefine $$k_1$$ as $$k_1 - x k_0$$ such that
$$k_1$$ has no time component. It will still give us $$k_0 \cdot k_1 = 0$$ and won't change $$u_{R0}$$, since we are talking about
