where $$ N $$ is

$$
\begin{eqnarray}
  &=& \not{l}\gamma^\mu\not{l} + ((1-y)\not{q}+z\not{p})\gamma^\mu(-y\not{q}+z\not{p}) + m^2\gamma^\mu + m(\not{q}\gamma^\mu+2(l^\mu-yq^\mu+zp^\mu))  \\
